data.description: REDUCED!!! Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Cantonment! This stunning residence boasts 5 bedrooms, three bathrooms, plus a flex space in primary and is situated on a sprawling acre of manicured grounds. This property offers a resort-style experience with its own private pool and a screened enclosure that ensures year-round enjoyment of the Florida sunshine. As you enter this grand home, you are greeted by a spacious and elegant foyer that sets the tone for the rest of the residence. The expansive living areas are bathed in natural light, creating an inviting and warm atmosphere. The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient layout that is perfect for both everyday living and entertaining guests. The five bedrooms are generously sized, providing plenty of space for family and guests. The primary suite is a true retreat, offering a peaceful haven with its own private en-suite bathroom, a separate flex room and 2 walk-in closets. The additional bedrooms are versatile, offering the flexibility to accommodate a variety of needs, from a home office to a fitness room. One of the highlights of this property is the outdoor oasis. Step outside to discover a large, sparkling pool surrounded by a screened enclosure, creating a tranquil and private setting. Whether you're hosting a poolside barbecue or simply enjoying a quiet evening under the stars, this space is designed for relaxation and entertainment. Situated on a full acre, the grounds of this home provide ample space for outdoor activities or amenities. The property is landscaped, creating a picturesque setting that enhances the overall appeal of this residence. Conveniently located in Cantonment, this home offers easy access to local amenities, schools, and parks. Enjoy the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience in this exceptional property. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home your own piece of paradise!
